    "description": "RVH Inc. engages in the beauty care, systems development, graphics, and solar energy businesses in Japan. It operates FLASH, an eyelash salon that provides eyelash extension services; and sells cosmetics, health food products, etc. The company also offers FVT-air, a medical image display software for medical institutions; system development services comprising embedded and IT systems development, inspection equipment solutions, and business management systems; and promotes and develops solar power plants on farmland, as well as engages in the revitalization of abandoned farmland and creation of agriculture related jobs. In addition, it provides solutions and support for IT, personnel, and security in the fields of temporary staffing, system development, and PC recycling; and business system development and IT support through a lean system development system, as well as staffing for system engineering and back office, PC data deletion, and recycling services. The company was formerly known as RealVision Inc. and changed its name to RVH Inc. in April 2015. RVH Inc. was incorporated in 1996 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
